HEADWORD: Apocopate
<hw>A*poc"o*pate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>apocopatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>apocopare</ets> to cut off, fr. L.
